{"id":"ozni","term":"Ozni","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Hearing, one of the sons of Gad; also called Ezbon (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 46:16\">Gen. 46:16</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 26:16\">Num. 26:16</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 46:16","Numbers 26:16"]}